      "text": "You always had to be one step.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe it's the way life was, which always-- I went to church.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
