      "text": "I can't think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I'm saying-- I'm saying all these things, I'm saying, did I really do all, did I live through all this?",
